{"type": "article", "id": 24603, "title": "彩色树脂家具", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-29T06:59:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702163756En3Bkcgu4LDsCiwx.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这组家具带给人童话的梦幻，纽约的女设计师 Kim Markel 使用再生塑料和树脂制作这些桌椅、镜子、花瓶等生活用品，它们结构简单而色彩单一，保留了打磨后的手工感，材料本身呈现出的半透明也令人想起一些甜品。镜子和花瓶可出售，其中像棒棒糖一样的镜子售价 120 美元，<a href=\"http://www.kimmarkel.com/shop/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021637537Mk3AzpXbhKlWUPZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163754NfMA9Dw3aZJo2Fbn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.01833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163754UzVvemQfYFI5RM0p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163755paZFQuLvfEmKe37q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702163755RbhpH0VS9tmBJfEW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}